item.title: Ep. 193: Moonlight Masquerade - Chapter 13 | #DND
item.description: In this week's episode the Dungeons & Dragons mayhem continues, with a mysterious corridor finally discovered, and a sudden fog, it's time to roll those Dnd Dice. Why does Keth keep taking damage? Where is this hidden foe? And when will they remember what they came here for? There's only one way to find out, join Tom (Keth), Paul (Milo), Alex (Derek), and Chip (Jeff), led by James (the Dungeon Master) and Roll Britannia. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/COMG8989578674
